Explainable Code Plagiarism Detection

A full-stack system for structured, explainable code similarity analysis with staged backend processing and interactive frontend visualization.

🛠 Tech Stack

Backend

FastAPI

PostgreSQL

SQLAlchemy

Pydantic

Uvicorn

Python 3.12+

Frontend

React (Vite)

JavaScript

npm

🚀 How to Run (Windows)
Backend

From project root:

cd backend

python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt

# set DATABASE_URL in .env

uvicorn app.main:app --reload

Backend runs at:

http://localhost:8000

Swagger docs:

http://localhost:8000/docs
Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev

Frontend runs at:

http://localhost:5173

CORS is configured to communicate with backend on port 8000.

